<p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 4px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 100 100 0%; height: auto; background-color: rgb(234, 230, 249);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 669px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 2;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2024年7月1日，在中国共产党103岁生日这天，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(141, 59, 151);">教育部正式批复同意江西软件职业技术大学新增办学地址，成立井冈山校区。</span></strong>这是继二十年前学校在英雄城南昌挂牌成立后，又一标志性重大喜讯，井冈山市也迎来家门口的第一所本科高校。这在学校办学历史和井冈山市经济社会发展中都有里程碑意义</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720490800054043145.png" title="1720490800054043145.png" alt="25a748743a4abb9e2c407bab11229601.png" style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 994px; height: 675px;" width="994" height="675"/><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 4px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 100 100 0%; height: auto; background-color: rgb(234, 230, 249);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 669px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 2;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">根据教育部的批复，江西软件职业技术大学的办学地址由原来的“江西省南昌市”<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(141, 59, 151);">扩展至“江西省南昌市、江西省井冈山市”。</span></strong>这一变更为学校在职业教育和数字经济领域提供了更广阔的发展空间，为井冈山市的数字经济发展和教育事业带来了新的机遇。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">教育部在批复中强调，江西省教育厅需依法履行管理服务职责，指导江西软件职业技术大学进一步改善办学条件，提高办学质量，服务地方经济社会发展。这表明教育部对学校未来发展的高度重视和期望。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720491290588057901.jpg" title="1720491290588057901.jpg" alt="e944150c448d1c87536544820c70563e.jpg" width="981" height="550" style="width: 981px; height: 550px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">据悉，2022年2月18日，</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(141, 59, 151);">井冈山市、先锋软件集团、江西软件职业技术大学三方签约，</span></strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">由先锋软件集团和学校总投资30亿元，建设占地1000亩先锋软件集团井冈山数字经济产业园和江西软件职业技术大学数字经济产业学院，完成了35万平方米的建筑工程量。</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(141, 59, 151);">在通过江西省普通高校设置评议委员会入规考察和院校设置考察、江西省政府批准调入规划、教育部备案审查和公示批复等环节后，江西软件职业技术大学井冈山校区正式成立。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(141, 59, 151);">江西软件职业技术大学是全国首批15所本科层次职业教育高校之一，现开设21个职业本科专业、22个高职专科专业。</span></strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">学校全面贯彻党的教育方针，始终坚持高等职业教育的属性和特色，秉承</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“创业创新、知识管理”</strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">校训，牢记</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“学好软件、报效祖国”</strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">使命，坚持</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“校企融合、产学互动”</strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">办学模式，实践</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“三好一专、十一工程”</strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">人才培养体系，形成了</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“用企业家育人理念培养学生”“请工程师当老师”“拿真实的项目进行实训”</strong><span style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">的校企深度融合发展路径，</span><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(141, 59, 151);">二十年来，累积为社会培养了近10万名数字经济领域的人才。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="text-indent: 2em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(141, 59, 151);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720491408435006378.png" title="1720491408435006378.png" alt="ae4a0f04cc32f0196c8d545624a435ad.png" width="979" height="562" style="width: 979px; height: 562px;"/></span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 50%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 338.5px; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; background-color: rgb(119, 39, 186);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 50%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 338.5px; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: right;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; vertical-align: top; overflow: hidden; background-color: rgb(119, 39, 186);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 4px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: auto; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 100 100 0%; height: auto; background-color: rgb(234, 230, 249);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 20px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 669px; vertical-align: top; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 2;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">江西软件职业技术大学井冈山校区的成立，将有助于推动井冈山的教育改革和创新，促进地方经济与社会的发展。学校将认真落实教育部的批复精神，在江西省委教育工委、江西省教育厅的领导和支持下，全力以赴推进新校区的建设和发展，努力建设有特色、<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">有品质、</span>有情怀、有作为的高水平职业技术大学，为国家培养更多高素质高层次技术技能型人才作贡献。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720491539925023611.png" title="1720491539925023611.png" alt="51cbf4b57918dc87a9c88eb48de859de.png" width="1" height="1" style="width: 1px; height: 1px;"/><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240709/1720491731891019969.png" title="1720491731891019969.png" alt="51cbf4b57918dc87a9c88eb48de859de.png" width="1022" height="579" style="width: 1022px; height: 579px;"/></p></section></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>